\begin_inset Formula \begin{equation}
\dot{\hat{z}}=A\hat{z}+\hat{\alpha}(y,H\hat{z},u)+l(y-c^{T}\hat{z}),\quad\hat{x}=S(\hat{z}).\label{eq:obs-aocf}\end{equation}

\end_inset

In general, the resulting error dynamics
