\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\alpha}$
\end_inset

 is Lipschitz, the observer gain 
\begin_inset Formula $l\in\R^{n}$
\end_inset

 may be calculated by high-gain techniques or passivity based approaches
 in order to stabilize the equilibrium point 
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{z}=0$
\end_inset

